T16:59:01.000Z","msg":"10/10"},{"pid":"e7d977abad2be9394347bb92bf1bc8c98b36b1ad","tid":1708630,"uid":70524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T16:59:06.000Z","msg":"分清奶共偽人同香港藝人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65799cef0830d6fa81c87b36a04aa4091212f806","tid":1708630,"uid":70724,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T17:02:15.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n順便係到警醒下班黃圈捉鬼小隊<br />\n要壯大個圈子就要海納百川<br />\n唔好小小事就踢人岀局<br />\n提供經濟誘因對某啲商户/人黎講係最吸引嘅事<br />\n唔好將自己崇高嘅道德標準加係每個人身上<br />\n到時比你踢曬岀局就得翻自己小圈子打飛機圍爐取暖"},{"pid":"8e904edbdcc5ee3dca0f29f385883156ca907b34","tid":1708630,"uid":46239,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T17:04:42.000Z","msg":"Share 下真香港藝人嘅新歌 大家支持下 多啲入去聽<br />\n<br />\n方皓玟 - 願<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4zNaEukzyGk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4zNaEukzyGk&d=KwnMNtvToZrWMgCiTfGJQVT2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=c8fe11dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4zNaEukzyGk</a><br />\n<br />\n許廷鏗 - 你可能未必不喜歡我<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/c4wwZP7idxo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fc4wwZP7idxo&d=KwnMNtvToZrWMgCiTfGJQVT2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=8d10e478\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/c4wwZP7idxo</a><br />\n<br />\n陳健安 - 在錯誤的宇宙尋找愛<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/2J_0nahRxBk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F2J_0nahRxBk&d=KwnMNtvToZrWMgCiTfGJQVT2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=952a0d8f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/2J_0nahRxBk</a>"},{"pid":"7185034e92c3c3924e96e4e513db62e05a374300","tid":1708630,"uid":70724,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T17:05:12.000Z","msg":"建立香港人本土市場 <br />\n令中資/親共萎縮係一場希望工程<br />\n但背後嘅影響可以係好大<br />\n亦係建立香港人本土意識最有力嘅工具"},{"pid":"e992a6d6bd84772674245974492aa1038ea44e0b","tid":1708630,"uid":46239,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"7185034e92c3c3924e96e4e513db62e05a374300","tid":1708630,"uid":70724,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T17:05:12.000Z","msg":"建立香港人本土市場 <br />\n令中資/親共萎縮係一場希望工程<br />\n但背後嘅影響可以係好大<br />\n亦係建立香港人本土意識最有力嘅工具"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T17:06:50.000Z","msg":"啱<br />\n中共最驚係啲藝人有第二條出路唔駛奶共"},{"pid":"074b713187982a9e4708054442a0d3337f7a300a","tid":1708630,"uid":46239,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T17:09:31.000Z","msg":"RubberBand - &iquest;醒未?<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/3zurCKJ84y4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F3zurCKJ84y4&d=KwnMNtvToZrWMgCiTfGJQVT2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=ec1edba1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/3zurCKJ84y4</a>"},{"pid":"06d4469cb48767bf1bcc0d72425b72d544b15d5e","tid":1708630,"uid":70724,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T17:10:37.000Z","msg":"之所以全世界商家/政府唔夠膽得罪支那畜<br />\n係因為佢地龐大嘅市場同購買力<br />\n極有骨氣嘅企業例外<br />\n香港人一定要認清一件事就係<br />\n唔係個個都咁有風骨<br />\n好多人都係利字行頭<br />\n想賺錢嘅就比人入黎黃圈<br />\n當圈子夠強壯嘅時候<br />\n佢地自然會遷就香港人<br />\n配合香港本土意識形態"},{"pid":"2321c15d68657ef8c6bd147f7307335709b3dca8","tid":1708630,"uid":46239,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"06d4469cb48767bf1bcc0d72425b72d544b15d5e","tid":1708630,"uid":70724,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T17:10:37.000Z","msg":"之所以全世界商家/政府唔夠膽得罪支那畜<br />\n係因為佢地龐大嘅市場同購買力<br />\n極有骨氣嘅企業例外<br />\n香港人一定要認清一件事就係<br />\n唔係個個都咁有風骨<br />\n好多人都係利字行頭<br />\n想賺錢嘅就比人入黎黃圈<br />\n當圈子夠強壯嘅時候<br />\n佢地自然會遷就香港人<br />\n配合香港本土意識形態"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T17:13:55.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n同埋香港文化絕對唔係淨係得大陸一個市場 <br />\n香港人咁叻 做出嚟嘅嘢放上國際舞台都好有吸引力<br />\n唔應該為咗大陸而限死自己"},{"pid":"af62b9856d73418ddc992ba3611b3f780962c8b8","tid":1708630,"uid":46239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T17:17:00.000Z","msg":"再自推十連"},{"pid":"453448ad43173762c473bf66b06b5817bca64bc6","tid":1708630,"uid":46239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T17:17:11.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"e3b843474e0dd87bfa18f25b40d9dc73c780de15","tid":1708630,"uid":46239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T17:17:24.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"2e0c658c077a6e24f931ed56e01b48aa7693556c","tid":1708630,"uid":46239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T17:17:37.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"d91d3b5501da61a6d73e0c1e91d505170580b165","tid":1708630,"uid":46239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T17:17:48.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"5bc32018d63ba004bf8329335a8af030371673fe","tid":1708630,"uid":46239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T17:17:58.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"c3d109523802981c5633487ff7870fd7ca195b60","tid":1708630,"uid":46239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T17:18:08.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"a9fbd63a34acde53fc8dc06da0e6d610ec537ead","tid":1708630,"uid":46239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T17:18:21.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"3592ea94d037bb84b65ea236a7079c798f594abf","tid":1708630,"uid":46239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T17:18:33.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"ada7c070eee3216e929da3075b55b332d21c46f8","tid":1708630,"uid":46239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T17:18:46.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"e6d824c1230995ee673eb840ce4217b0c12f96ec","tid":1708630,"uid":46239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T17:18:57.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"3ed7068ac675b889c50b893c29a083e654fbd62d","tid":1708630,"uid":46239,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T17:22:31.000Z","msg":"除咗電影同音樂<br />\n仲有手機game<br />\n雖然係抄game<br />\n但如果係企係我地呢邊<br />\n都撐<br />\n神魔之塔：管理層將與香港人同行，並停止更新專頁<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1708645\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1708645</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"p